WEBVTT

00:03:29.667 --> 00:03:32.684
va shifoxonalaridagi 
onlayn portallari ham.

00:03:32.708 --> 00:03:35.059
Ularni internetli o'yinchoqlar, 
ularning onlayn

00:03:35.083 --> 00:03:36.393
o'yinlari orqali
kuzatishadi

00:03:36.417 --> 00:03:39.083
va boshqa judayam ko'plab
texnologiyalar orqali.

00:03:40.250 --> 00:03:41.893
Tadqiqotim davomida

00:03:41.917 --> 00:03:46.059
ko'plab ota-onalar oldimga kelishardi
va "Ho'sh nima bo'libdi?" deyishardi.

00:03:46.083 --> 00:03:49.000
"Nima farqi bor bolalarim kuzatilishini?

00:03:50.042 --> 00:03:51.375
Yashiradigan narsamiz yo'q."

00:03:52.958 --> 00:03:54.458
Lekin, farqi bor.

00:03:55.083 --> 00:04:01.101
Farqi bor, chunki hozirda odamlarni 
nafaqat kuzatishadi,